settings.title: Designed with real parents’ feedback, The Manual Glider is the ultimate nursery glider for the modern parent.
Mom’s New Best Friend
settings.text: Postpartum is no joke, regardless of what kind of delivery you have, and our gliders not only keeps you off your feet, but also keeps your baby fuss-free with the features that we hand-picked to help out new parents. Win-win, right?

settings.title: From the early morning rocks to midnight feedings, we’ve got you covered.
settings.text: You can expect to spend almost 1,000 hours rocking or feeding your baby in his or her first six months. We’ve got you covered whether it’s hour 1 - or hour 999 - by supporting you and your baby with our unique features and providing you with the comfort you deserve.
Join our community for inspiration, tips & tricks, and more.
